.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15460] bumped array-init-cursor from 0.2.0 to 0.2.1
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15418] bumped crate-ci/typos from 1.29.10 to 1.30.3
.
